item.title: Machete
item.description: Those scum ridden sacks of shit didn’t even have the empathy to honorably discharge me. I was just told to shut up and get out. I cleared a tech base of those nightmares and I bet they’d still rather see me dead than holding a place in the marines again. I don’t need help, I just need to wipe out the rest of these terrors and get rid of that awful noise. Onward to Sunveil Starport.
